<h2 class="centered padded-title">This is not a job board.</h2>

<div class="arguments-container">
  <div class="arguments col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6">
    <div class="argument-box card-1" style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'oneclick.png', crop: :fill; %>') ;">
      <dl>
        <dt><h4 class="centered why-title">Reclaim Your Time</h4></dt>
        <dd>Import info from LinkedIn or a resume.<br><br>Complete your profile in less than 60 seconds.<br><br>Apply to jobs in 1 click.</dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
</div>

  <div class="arguments col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6">
    <div class="argument-box card-2" style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'chalkboard.png', crop: :fill; %>') ;">
      <dl>
        <dt><h4 class="centered why-title">Search by your values </h4></dt>
        <dd>Filter by paternal leave, beach access, salary, a Scala backend, or all of the above. <br><br>No one will see your information unless YOU agree it's a fit. </dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="arguments col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
    <div class="argument-box card-3" style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'importlinkedin.png', crop: :fill; %>') ;">
     <dl>
      <dt><h4 class="centered why-title">Prioritize relationships</h4></dt>
      <dd>Our algorithm gets all the boring parts out of the way. When you apply to a role, one of our career coaches will jump on the phone, answer any questions you have, and help you prep for interviews. You only have to focus on how you feel talking to your new potential team.</dd>
    </dl>
  </div>
</div>



